name: Here/After The Art NFT Mint Pass

metadata.name: Here/After The Art NFT Mint Pass
metadata.description: The Here/After The Art NFT Mint Pass provides an exclusive opportunity to acquire a 1/1 NFT prior to the public and at a special price. Only 10 are available. The entire project is limited to 100 unique NFTs. This is a priceless chance to interact with visionary artists and their predictions for the future of art.
